-al-safr","tag-weakness-al-daf","tag-wellness-al-afiyah"],"aioseo_notices":[],"jetpack_featured_media_url":"","jetpack_shortlink":"https:\/\/wp.me\/p95VHY-6SR","jetpack_sharing_enabled":true,"jetpack-related-posts":[{"id":26422,"url":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/2018\/05\/16\/abu-darda-loneliness-evil-friend\/","url_meta":{"origin":26465,"position":0},"title":"Abu Darda on Friends: Loneliness is better than an evil companion","author":"Abu Amina Elias","date":"May 16, 2018","format":false,"excerpt":"Ibn Hibban reported: Abu Darda, may Allah be pleased with him, said, \u201cA righteous companion is better than loneliness, and loneliness is better than an evil companion. A good writer is better than one silent, and one silent is better than an evil writer.\u201d Source: Rawd\u0323at al-\u2018Uqala\u0304' 56 \u0639\u0646 \u0627\u0628\u0646\u2026","rel":"","context":"In &quot;Scholars \u0627\u0644\u0639\u0644\u0645\u0627\u0621&quot;","block_context":{"text":"Scholars \u0627\u0644\u0639\u0644\u0645\u0627\u0621","link":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/category\/scholars-ulema\/"},"img":{"alt_text":"","src":"","width":0,"height":0},"classes":[]},{"id":15463,"url":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/2013\/07\/29\/dangers-travel-alone\/","url_meta":{"origin":26465,"position":1},"title":"Hadith on Safety: Dangerous to travel alone at night","author":"Abu Amina Elias","date":"July 29, 2013","format":false,"excerpt":"Ibn Umar reported: The Prophet, peace and blessings be upon him, said, \u201cIf people knew what I knew about traveling alone, no one would set out alone at night.\u201d Source: S\u0323ah\u0323i\u0304h\u0323 al-Bukha\u0304ri\u0304 2998 Grade: Sahih (authentic) according to Al-Bukhari \u0639\u064e\u0646\u0652 \u0627\u0628\u0652\u0646\u0650 \u0639\u064f\u0645\u064e\u0631\u064e \u0639\u064e\u0646\u0652 \u0627\u0644\u0646\u064e\u0651\u0628\u0650\u064a\u0650\u0651 \u0635\u064e\u0644\u064e\u0651\u0649 \u0627\u0